{"tid":1996802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃金週爆買唔係您諗得咁簡單","createTime":"2020-05-01T07:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T08:44:20.000Z","uid":45991,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"01b63edc77c235ba392507f5bb706f1ec9ccc156","tid":1996802,"uid":45991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:57:56.000Z","msg":"自己要買要食要撐黃店係好基本<br />\n但點樣令到您身邊嘅藍都比錢黃店洗先係進一步昇華返件事<br />\n唔一定要帶佢地去食 逼佢地睇文宣 咁樣又會搵交嘈大家無野好講背脊骨落<br />\n<br />\n黃店緊有一間係附近<br />\n夜晚係屋企叫您藍絲老豆老母坐定定<br />\n之後叫個黃店外賣 <br />\n咁樣黃店就由一人份量訂單變成三人份量既訂單<br />\n您又可以扮下乖仔乖女塞飽藍絲廢老把口同時又可以幫黃店搵多啲<br />\n大家都有著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b504874c949bb3d3f12d52e212dd9141119598b","tid":1996802,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f11f3dd91549bad5202ebd9445a4a4d0a38e0e1","tid":1996802,"uid":223643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:01:08.000Z","msg":"同埋大家可以感染下身邊嘅同輩<br />\n令到佢哋覺得食黃店係一件好型嘅事"},{"pid":"acb0ec06756ab67ee34ee1fa58946df32bbf2213","tid":1996802,"uid":62270,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:06:10.000Z","msg":"我地只係買野唔講政治，同埋平靚正所以幫襯"},{"pid":"5db5d40b807378dc4ad9abdc339beb8d35865da6","tid":1996802,"uid":45991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f11f3dd91549bad5202ebd9445a4a4d0a38e0e1","tid":1996802,"uid":223643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:01:08.000Z","msg":"同埋大家可以感染下身邊嘅同輩<br />\n令到佢哋覺得食黃店係一件好型嘅事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:07:15.000Z","msg":"啱！同輩前輩後輩都要<br />\n唔好只係同同路人手足自己友去食 <br />\n要壯大就要拎埋藍同綠個餅 <br />\n要拎埋佢地個餅就係要搵多啲唔同人去食去買"},{"pid":"0cb59d2cfcd722ffadebf565123c7c2391e8b63a","